Class ConnectionTest

java.lang.Object
  test.Test
      conformance.rmi.ConnectionTest

public class ConnectionTest
extends Test

Tests complete connection between stub and skeleton.

This test starts a skeleton. Two stubs are then created - one implicitly from the skeleton, and one by specifying the address directly. Both stubs are then tested by calling a method in each. The test covers the passing of arguments, transmission of return values, and transmission of remote exceptions.
